    "notes": "Note that you don't need to hold the Kingdom of Thessalonika title, only all its counties. Replace the Byzantine emperor from 1066 with a custom character of French culture and Catholic faith and traits that will offset the Opinion loss. Find a way to conquer enough territory from Hungary and Pechenegs to create the Empire of Carpathia. Then destroy the Byzantine Empire title.\n\nAlternatively, after completing Miklagarðaríki (if you have the [![DLC Northern Lords.png](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/c/c5/DLC_Northern_Lords.png/24px-DLC_Northern_Lords.png)](/Northern_Lords \"Northern Lords\") Northern Lords DLC), move your capital to France and convert to the local faith and culture to get the achievement instantly."
