    "completionRequirements": "![Yes](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/0f/Icon_check.png/24px-Icon_check.png) Is independent\n\n![Yes](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/0f/Icon_check.png/24px-Icon_check.png) All dynasty members except the player is not landed or an independent ruler",
    "notes": "In 1066 play as Count Herbert of Vermandois, a vassal of France and the only landed Karling. Declare an independence war and surrender. There is a chance that you will be banished as an adventurer, which will instantly unlock the achievement."
