    "completionRequirements": "![Yes](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/0f/Icon_check.png/24px-Icon_check.png) At least 10 dynasty members are independent and own a ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/01/Kingdom.png/24px-Kingdom.png) Kingdom title or higher.",
    "notes": "In 867 replace the khagan of Kirghiz with a custom ruler with 9 sons and whatever traits are beneficial. You start completely controlling the de jure territory of 3 kingdoms and half of two more. The Kirghiz Khanate does not have any de jure territory so you can grant independence to any kingdom. Create the kingdoms you already control and conquer more, then give them to your sons and grant them independence all together."
