    "completionRequirements": "![Yes](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/0f/Icon_check.png/24px-Icon_check.png) Knows 10 languages",
    "notes": "Create a 21 years old custom character with the ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/3/3e/Trait_education_learning_5.png/24px-Trait_education_learning_5.png) Erudite Oracle trait and put the remaining points into ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/2/22/Learning.png/24px-Learning.png) Learning.\n\nChoose a culture with the \"**Astute Diplomats**\" tradition for the +1 foreign language limit and +25% Learn Language Scheme Power (Franconian, German, Nubian, Volhynian, Öngüd, Croatian, Bolghar) or with \"**Culture Blending**\" for the +30% Learn Language Scheme Power and +1 Max Learn Language Schemes (Mon, Gond, Kamrupi, Avar, Merya, Meshchera, Muroma).\n\n  \nUse the free perks to get the Pedagogy and Open-Minded perks. Use the Learn Language scheme to learn more languages. Choose a diplomacy lifestyle and get the Adaptive Traditions perk for an extra scheme. You can also convert to a culture with a different language or hybridize with one to instantly learn its language."
