    "notes": "In 867 replace the king of France with a character of Basque culture, ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/c/c8/Trait_cynical.png/24px-Trait_cynical.png) Cynical trait, and traits that give ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/04/Icon_prestige_01.png/24px-Icon_prestige_01.png) Prestige and ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/f/fa/Icon_piety_christian_01.png/24px-Icon_piety_christian_01.png) Piety. You will already hold the required counties. Raise ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/0/04/Icon_prestige_01.png/24px-Icon_prestige_01.png) Prestige and ![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/f/fa/Icon_piety_christian_01.png/24px-Icon_piety_christian_01.png) Piety to 1000 each and use the Champion the Faith of the Country Basques decision."
