    "description": "Create and rule Valencia as an heir to El Cid. May not be available for characters created in the Ruler Designer.",
    "icon": "https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/2/2f/Legacy_of_the_champeadores_achievement.png/64px-Legacy_of_the_champeadores_achievement.png",
