    "notes": "The decision is only available if starting in 867. Play as Silla, conquer the only specific county left in the game that you need (which just so happens to be conveniently independent), then conquer whatever your heart desires until your realm is large enough to take the decision. Conquest of parts of China is possible once Tang explodes, and could be potentially combined with various Chinese achievements from the list below, if you so choose."
