    "completionRequirements": "![](https://ck3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/d/d9/Hegemony.png/24px-Hegemony.png) Owns the Hegemony of China title",
    "notes": "The main part of this achievement is to get to China in time before you die or it explodes. You can use the Adventure CB more than once, to make sure you're out of range for the King of France which will try his best to kill you. You can use the regular \"take county\" CB to puncture your way, hopping from county to county (e.g. Dalmatia -> Sinai -> Oman -> Gujarat -> Bengal -> Vietnam). Try to not use your special units as they don't repopulate. Once you border China you will get the Claim the Mandate CB. Use it, use your armies strategically to defeat an enemy, then take some land and you can enforce demands, getting the achievement\n\nNote that despite the achievement being worded as \"Starting as Hæsteinn\" it is actually \"Playing as Hæsteinn\"."
