    "notes": "Can be combined with Fishing in China achievement.\n\nPlaying as Hæsteinn, conquer the county of [Kanara](/List_of_counties#Kanara \"List of counties\") (holy site for Nestorianism). Once you have the Claim the Mandate CB, start the war, make as many prisoners as possible and execute them to reach a piety score of 7-8000 - Getting the Apostate trait helps too. When you are ready to enforce demands, convert to Nestorianism, then create a new christian faith with you as temporal head of faith."
